<blockquote> <p>Competencies: Written communication, Self development- pursuing and applying feedback, multi-tasking in a fast-paced environment, maintaining a successful personal brand while providing critical feedback,
        Professionalism - Being present and prepared, prioritizing and completing tasks to accomplish goals.</p> 
        <p>Students have a limited timeframe to develop one of three drawing styles into an acrylic painting. Students must explain, through written critique, what the style, color, and composition convey to the viewer about themselves.</p></blockquote>

</worksheet>
